
Ranger Help for: torch
======================

SYNTAX:      torch arrow/bolt
USAGE:       forest,plains,jungle,swamp,beach
SLOT COST:   5
BASE SP:     15 sp
SKILL TYPE:  arrow

SUMMARY:    
This skill allows a Ranger to take an arrow or bolt and set it a blaze.
Flaming arrows do a good deal more damage than plain or other enhanced
arrows or bolts. Arrows are used in shortbows and longbows, while bolts
are used in crossbows. Flaming arrows only last for so long, and then 
they burn up.

